stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> Sending : Send Message
    Sending --> AwaitingAck : Await Acknowledgment
    AwaitingAck --> Delivered : Acknowledgment Received
    AwaitingAck --> Resending : No Acknowledgment
    Resending --> Sending : Resend Message
    Delivered --> [*]
    Resending --> AwaitingAck : Await Acknowledgment
    Resending --> Idle : Max Retries Exceeded